"This release includes bug fixes to improve robustness and user experience"
" as well as a fix for the security vulnerability described in `our "
"February 11th, 2020 news post </news/security/istio-security-2020-001>`_."
" This release note describes what’s different between Istio 1.4.3 and "
"Istio 1.4.4."
msgstr ""

