#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:13
msgid "Security update"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:15
msgid ""
"**ISTIO-SECURITY-2020-001** An improper input validation has been "
"discovered in ``AuthenticationPolicy``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"`CVE-2020-8595 <https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-"
"bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2020-8595>`_: A bug in Istio’s `Authentication "
"Policy "
"</docs/reference/config/security/istio.authentication.v1alpha1/#Policy>`_"
" exact path matching logic allows unauthorized access to resources "
"without a valid JWT token."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:25
msgid "Bug fixes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Fixed** Debian packaging of ``iptables`` scripts (`Issue 19615 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/19615>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Fixed** an issue where Pilot generated a wrong Envoy configuration when"
" the same port was used more than once (`Issue 19935 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/19935>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:32
msgid ""
"**Fixed** an issue where running multiple instances of Pilot could lead "
"to a crash (`Issue 20047 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/20047>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Fixed** a potential flood of configuration pushes from Pilot to Envoy "
"when scaling the deployment to zero (`Issue 17957 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/17957>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Fixed** an issue where Mixer could not fetch the correct information "
"from the request/response when pod contains a dot in its name (`Issue "
"20028 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/20028>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:41
msgid ""
"**Fixed** an issue where Pilot sometimes would not send a correct pod "
"configuration to Envoy (`Issue 19025 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/19025>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:44
msgid ""
"**Fixed** an issue where sidecar injector with SDS enabled was "
"overwriting pod ``securityContext`` section, instead of just patching it "
"(`Issue 20409 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/20409>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:49
msgid "Improvements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:51
msgid ""
"**Improved** Better compatibility with Google CA. (Issues `20530 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/20530>`_, `20560 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/20560>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.4.x/announcing-1.4.4/index.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Improved** Added analyzer error message when Policies using JWT are not"
" configured properly (Issues `20884 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/20884>`_, `20767 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/20767>`_)."
msgstr ""

